parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the worm gear shaft can cause a rubbing or whirring noise in the steering column, which can lead to a loss of steering control, potentially causing accidents or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause a loss of steering control, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lower ball joint can cause a loss of steering control, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
